 and deliverables will all be agreed upon in the project contract with Millettech.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Increase project management capabilities</b>.\r\n    An experienced software project outsourcing company like Millettech understands and utilizes project management principles. These are fully integrated into the process we use to deliver your project to you. The skills can be added to your own to ensure the successful completion of your project.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Improve efficiency of in-house staff allocation. </b>\r\n    Scheduling of your resources is more efficient since in-house personnel can be assigned to current, critical, or ongoing projects. Finding time for a new project can be difficult when current in-house resources are being utilized to their maximum capabilities, while outsourcing it would gain you equivalent benefit.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Timely project implementation and completion</b>.\r\n    A well-defined and planned project would be delivered within the timeline set out in the project documentation provided by Millettech. \r\n    Having a team dedicated to the software project outsourcing eliminates the need to pull staff when more urgent or daily issues arise. When the project is outsourced to Millettech, in-house work can be better managed, and the completion date of your project will not be affected by day-to-day in-house issues.</li>\r\n</ul><br>','Software Offshore Outsourcing','','publish','closed','closed','','software-offshore-outsourcing','','','2018-01-19 15:16:34','2018-01-19 07:16:34','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=114',0,'page','',0),(115,1,'2018-01-19 15:16:34','2018-01-19 07:16:34','<p>Millettech is an experienced software project outsourcing service provider with a pool of high tech professionals. By outsourcing to Millettech, you may enjoy:</p>\r\n<ul type=\"square\">\r\n    <li><b>Access to an experienced team.</b>\r\n    Millettech has a team of highly experienced software project developers with average 6 years work