tal Development \r\n</li><li>E-commerce, Secure Transactions \r\n</li><li>E-branding \r\n</li><li>Database integration \r\n</li><li>ASP,.NET, PHP, XML, DHTML, JAVA, PERL, C/C++, and VB \r\n</li><li>EDI, ERP \r\n</li><li>Quality Assurance and Testing \r\n</li><li>Online Media (Audio, Video) \r\n</li><li>Systems Integration </li></ul></div><br>','E-commerce','','inherit','closed','closed','','121-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:20:10','2018-01-19 07:20:10','',121,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=122',0,'revision','',0),(123,1,'2018-01-19 15:20:51','2018-01-19 07:20:51','<p>Millettech provides domain name registration services. We offer a full turn-key package that includes web design, web promotion, software development, web hosting<font color=\"#0000ff\"> </font>and domain names registration. Domain Name is also known as \'web address\'. </p>\r\n<p>The Domain Name System (DNS) translates the numerical addresses of computers into more user- friendly names. The resulting domain names are easy toremember and help people to find information on the Internet very easily. Every domain name is unique. This is why it is important to register your chosen domains before anyone else does. Even if you do not intend to implement your website in the near future, it is highly recommended you register your chosen business or website name to avoid it being taken. </p>\r\n<p>Choosing the right domain name for your business is of paramount importance. Potential clients are unlikely to be willing to trust a company who will not even purchase their own domain, especially when it comes to credit card details. Therefore, take care to choose a domain name that reflects your company,and encourages trust and professionalism. </p>\r\n<p>The other main idea to consider is making the domain name easy for surfers to find. An obscure name is completely useless. You should aim at a name short and memorable. Take care to consider your target audience. If you intend to implement your website in the near future, we will register your domain name and web hosting service at the same time, allowing immediate development of your site.</p>\r\n<p><span>Millettech offers domain name consultation and registration as part of our design packages. If you choose to take up our design solutions, we can offer qualified advice on how to choose a domain that will benefit your business to the greatest extent. </span></p><br>','Domain Name Registration','','publish','closed','closed','','domain-name-registration','','','2018-01-19 15:20:51','2018-01-19 07:20:51','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=123',0,'page','',0),(124,1,'2018-01-19 15:20:51','2018-01-19 07:20:51','<p>Millettech provides domain name registration services. We offer a full turn-key package that includes web design, web promotion, software development, web hosting<font color=\"#0000ff\"> </font>and domain names registration. Domain Name is also known as \'web address\'. </p>\r\n<p>The Domain Name System (DNS) translates the numerical addresses of computers into more user- friendly names. The resulting domain names are easy toremember and help people to find information on the Internet very easily. Every domain name is unique. This is why it is important to register your chosen domains before anyone else does. Even if you do not intend to implement your website in the near future, it is highly recommended you register your chosen business or website name to avoid it being taken. </p>\r\n<p>Choosing the right domain name for your business is of paramount importance. Potential clients are unlikely to be willing to trust a company who will not even purchase their own domain, especially when it comes to credit card details. Therefore, take care to choose a domain name that reflects your company,and encourages trust and professionalism. </p>\r\n<p>The other main idea to consider is making the domain name easy for surfers to find. An obscure name is completely useless. You should aim at a name short and memorable. Take care to consider your target audience. If you intend to implement your website in the near future, we will register your domain name and web hosting service at the same time, allowing immediate development of your site.</p>\r\n<p><span>Millettech offers domain name consultation and registration as part of our design packages. If you choose to take up our design solutions, we can offer qualified advice on how to choose a domain that will benefit your business to the greatest extent. </span></p><br>','Domain Name Registration','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:20:51','2018-01-19 07:20:51','',123,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=124',0,'revision','',0),(125,1,'2018-01-19 15:21:28','2018-01-19 07:21:28','<p>The function of search engines and the procedures for the submission, registration and listing with them is important for the promotion of your website! Millettech has done considerable researches on this. <br><br>There are thousands of websites created each day, so competition for ranking is fierce. There are no real shortcuts to achieve a high ranking, it is a complex process and varies from site to site. It is important to note that search engines and web directories are different and that a different approach is necessary to achieve listing in both. Search engine registration should follow a schedule for maximum effectiveness. Each search engine is unique and requires research to get to the best positions. This is why those services that promise to \"submit your site to 3000 search engines\" do not work- besides, how many search engines do you use? <br><br>The results of a survey of website marketers have found that most prefer to submit manually to search engines rather than use auto-submission tools. Most marketers said that this was because they \"know\" manual submission is more effective. <br><br>Millettech strongly recommend that search engine registration is made by a regular continuous process. The reason for this is that search engines have a habit of dropping sites without warning. The remedy may simply be a re-submission and Millettech will take care of this for you when we encounter rankings which are not good enough (usually if your site is out of the top 30). <br><br>Also, search engines will change their ranking methods from time to time and this can take the same effect. One moment, your site could be doing well, ranking in the top 10, until a search engine decides to change its algorithm and you drop down several pages allowing your competitors to take your place. Such an event may need a re-think about your site\'s optimization. You cannot do this until you know that you have dropped down the list, hence the importance of monitoring your site\'s rankings. <br><br><br>Our search engine registration and search engine placement services will enable your website to get your requested positions in the major search engines. </p><br>','Search Engine Registration','','publish','closed','closed','','search-engine-registration','','','2018-01-19 15:21:28','2018-01-19 07:21:28','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=125',0,'page','',0),(126,1,'2018-01-19 15:21:28','2018-01-19 07:21:28','<p>The function of search engines and the procedures for the submission, registration and listing with them is important for the promotion of your website! Millettech has done considerable researches on this. <br><br>There are thousands of websites created each day, so competition for ranking is fierce. There are no real shortcuts to achieve a high ranking, it is a complex process and varies from site to site. It is important to note that search engines and web directories are different and that a different approach is necessary to achieve listing in both. Search engine registration should follow a schedule for maximum effectiveness. Each search engine is unique and requires research to get to the best positions. This is why those services that promise to \"submit your site to 3000 search engines\" do not work- besides, how many search engines do you use? <br><br>The results of a survey of website marketers have found that most prefer to submit manually to search engines rather than use auto-submission tools. Most marketers said that this was because they \"know\" manual submission is more effective. <br><br>Millettech strongly recommend that search engine registration is made by a regular continuous process. The reason for this is that search engines have a habit of dropping sites without warning. The remedy may simply be a re-submission and Millettech will take care of this for you when we encounter rankings which are not good enough (usually if your site is out of the top 30). <br><br>Also, search engines will change their ranking methods from time to time and this can take the same effect. One moment, your site could be doing well, ranking in the top 10, until a search engine decides to change its algorithm and you drop down several pages allowing your competitors to take your place. Such an event may need a re-think about your site\'s optimization. You cannot do this until you know that you have dropped down the list, hence the importance of monitoring your site\'s rankings. <br><br><br>Our search engine registration and search engine placement services will enable your website to get your requested positions in the major search engines. </p><br>','Search Engine Registration','','inherit','closed','closed','','125-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:21:28','2018-01-19 07:21:28','',125,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=126',0,'revision','',0),(127,1,'2018-01-19 15:22:30','2018-01-19 07:22:30','<p>Millettech is a full service Search Engine Optimization Company. We do more than search engine submission, placement and build PageRank. SEO services involve facilitating link building, keyword research as well as SEO friendly website development. <br><br>Search Engine Optimization is a broad definition for the various methods in which websites can be created, designed, and maintained with the intention of being indexed and ranked within search engines and online directories. <br><br>Search Engine Optimization is perhaps the single most important feature in a company\'s Internet strategy. Companies often put substantial effort in building their websites but place inadequate emphasis on SEO services. The objective of search engine optimization services is to help a company get better rankings in the search engines. <br>As always the search engine algorithms change very frequently, a trick working today may not work tomorrow. Hence we believe in laying a strong foundation for our SEO campaigns. <br>Search engine optimization services can be broadly separated into the following categories: </p>\r\n<ul type=\"square\">\r\n<li>Identifying the right Keywords \r\n</li><li>Formulating a meta content strategy \r\n</li><li>Creating search engine friendly Content \r\n</li><li>Designing a search engine friendly Layout \r\n</li><li>Taking care of images and links \r\n</li><li>Ensuring link popularity \r\n</li><li>Formulating a Submission strategy </li></ul><br>','Search Engine Optimization','','publish','closed','closed','','search-engine-optimization','','','2018-01-19 15:22:30','2018-01-19 07:22:30','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=127',0,'page','',0),(128,1,'2018-01-19 15:22:30','2018-01-19 07:22:30','<p>Millettech is a full service Search Engine Optimization Company. We do more than search engine submission, placement and build PageRank. SEO services involve facilitating link building, keyword research as well as SEO friendly website development. <br><br>Search Engine Optimization is a broad definition for the various methods in which websites can be created, designed, and maintained with the intention of being indexed and ranked within search engines and online directories. <br><br>Search Engine Optimization is perhaps the single most important feature in a company\'s Internet strategy. Companies often put substantial effort in building their websites but place inadequate emphasis on SEO services. The objective of search engine optimization services is to help a company get better rankings in the search engines. <br>As always the search engine algorithms change very frequently, a trick working today may not work tomorrow. Hence we believe in laying a strong foundation for our SEO campaigns. <br>Search engine optimization services can be broadly separated into the following categories: </p>\r\n<ul type=\"square\">\r\n<li>Identifying the right Keywords \r\n</li><li>Formulating a meta content strategy \r\n</li><li>Creating search engine friendly Content \r\n</li><li>Designing a search engine friendly Layout \r\n</li><li>Taking care of images and links \r\n</li><li>Ensuring link popularity \r\n</li><li>Formulating a Submission strategy </li></ul><br>','Search Engine Optimization','','inherit','closed','closed','','127-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:22:30','2018-01-19 07:22:30','',127,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=128',0,'revision','',0),(129,1,'2018-01-19 15:23:29','2018-01-19 07:23:29','<p><b>1. Portals and EAI</b></p>\r\n<p><b>Overview</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The Millettech, Portals and EAI Technical Service, is focusing on consolidating corporate resources by helping corporate clients to integrate multiple applications. Our practices include: Enterprise Information Portal, Enterprise Application Integration, and Content Management.</p>\r\n<p><b>Enterprise</b><b> Information Portal (EIP)</b></p>\r\n<p>Millettech help companies build Portals to effectively streamline and integrate access to applications, documents, and internet services through a single web site for anyone to use anywhere. Portals improve productivity across the enterprise and directly support IT cost reductions in areas such as network and storage, web infrastructure, intranet and extranet administration, training, and communication.</p>\r\n<p><b>Enterprise</b><b> Application Integration (EAI)</b></p>\r\n<p>Enterprise Integration uses technologies and Web services standards to connect and streamline business processes, systems, and information, and creates a strong information foundation that can help move organizations toward higher performance. Millettech\'s collaborative approach enables effective integration of business processes to help organizations access, manage and exploit data to make more informed business decisions.</p>\r\n<p><a name=\"4\"></a><b>ECM ( Enterprise Content Management) </b></p>\r\n<p>Millettech\'s web content management services range from managing the content lifecycle to technical implementation. Enterprise content management covers document management, electronic forms, imaging, digital media and integration solutions. \r\nOur Enterprise Content Management solution framework is intended to help you define a holistic enterprise content management strategy and implement an integrated solution. We can plan, design and implement cost effective solutions to aid you in community building, collaboration, content publishing and back-office integration. \r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><b>2. OA Management</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>OA management of Millettech is actually different from the traditional one .The purpose of OA management is to improve the company\'s efficiency and help get rid of part of the manual work. The traditional OA management is limited in the width and depth of information so that the information is hard to be transformed to knowledge, let alone a knowledge management system.. So our company makes use of the modern OA management to collect knowledge hidden in information and sets up a knowledge management system to transform reserve and deploy the knowledge.</p>\r\n<p><b>3. Customer Relationship Management </b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Millettech always considers the relationship between customers is not to be managed but to share commons with them and think for them at any time. We have basic principles of observing, engaging and empathizing with our customers, to develop ideas that solve their real needs. Customers are our gods and we do everything to make them satisfied.</p>\r\n<p><b>4. Content Management System</b></p>\r\n<p>PHPCMS is a website system based on PHP and MYSQL. After being improved, it is applicable to many environments such as UNIX, LINUX, and WINDONWS. And it can provide website solutions with high efficiency and quality. This system includes four modules: text, download, images and news, supporting content charge, advertisement management and the forum integration. Mellettech has successfully developed a new edition of content management system (CMS 1.2). CMS 1.2 is mainly for Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Website Management, Multiple Language, FTP, Template, E-commerce, and Online Pay pal Payment, etc. CMS 1.2 can integrate companies of small or middle scale which have a good perspective.</p><br>','IT Solution','','publish','closed','closed','','it-solution','','','2018-01-19 15:23:29','2018-01-19 07:23:29','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=129',0,'page','',0),(130,1,'2018-01-19 15:23:29','2018-01-19 07:23:29','<p><b>1. Portals and EAI</b></p>\r\n<p><b>Overview</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The Millettech, Portals and EAI Technical Service, is focusing on consolidating corporate resources by helping corporate clients to integrate multiple applications. Our practices include: Enterprise Information Portal, Enterprise Application Integration, and Content Management.</p>\r\n<p><b>Enterprise</b><b> Information Portal (EIP)</b></p>\r\n<p>Millettech help companies build Portals to effectively streamline and integrate access to applications, documents, and internet services through a single web site for anyone to use anywhere. Portals improve productivity across the enterprise and directly support IT cost reductions in areas such as network and storage, web infrastructure, intranet and extranet administration, training, and communication.</p>\r\n<p><b>Enterprise</b><b> Application Integration (EAI)</b></p>\r\n<p>Enterprise Integration uses technologies and Web services standards to connect and streamline business processes, systems, and information, and creates a strong information foundation that can help move organizations toward higher performance. Millettech\'s collaborative approach enables effective integration of business processes to help organizations access, manage and exploit data to make more informed business decisions.</p>\r\n<p><a name=\"4\"></a><b>ECM ( Enterprise Content Management) </b></p>\r\n<p>Millettech\'s web content management services range from managing the content lifecycle to technical implementation. Enterprise content management covers document management, electronic forms, imaging, digital media and integration solutions. \r\nOur Enterprise Content Management solution framework is intended to help you define a holistic enterprise content management strategy and implement an integrated solution. We can plan, design and implement cost effective solutions to aid you in community building, collaboration, content publishing and back-office integration. \r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><b>2. OA Management</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>OA management of Millettech is actually different from the traditional one .The purpose of OA management is to improve the company\'s efficiency and help get rid of part of the manual work. The traditional OA management is limited in the width and depth of information so that the information is hard to be transformed to knowledge, let alone a knowledge management system.. So our company makes use of the modern OA management to collect knowledge hidden in information and sets up a knowledge management system to transform reserve and deploy the knowledge.</p>\r\n<p><b>3. Customer Relationship Management </b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Millettech always considers the relationship between customers is not to be managed but to share commons with them and think for them at any time. We have basic principles of observing, engaging and empathizing with our customers, to develop ideas that solve their real needs. Customers are our gods and we do everything to make them satisfied.</p>\r\n<p><b>4. Content Management System</b></p>\r\n<p>PHPCMS is a website system based on PHP and MYSQL. After being improved, it is applicable to many environments such as UNIX, LINUX, and WINDONWS. And it can provide website solutions with high efficiency and quality. This system includes four modules: text, download, images and news, supporting content charge, advertisement management and the forum integration. Mellettech has successfully developed a new edition of content management system (CMS 1.2). CMS 1.2 is mainly for Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Website Management, Multiple Language, FTP, Template, E-commerce, and Online Pay pal Payment, etc. CMS 1.2 can integrate companies of small or middle scale which have a good perspective.</p><br>','IT Solution','','inherit','closed','closed','','129-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:23:29','2018-01-19 07:23:29','',129,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=130',0,'revision','',0),(131,1,'2018-01-19 15:24:22','2018-01-19 07:24:22','<p><b>Technical Consulting</b></p>\r\n<p><b>PHP Application Consulting</b></p>\r\n<p>PHP is world\'s fastest growing web development language and Millettech specializes in this scripting language. We have many years experience in website designing and development with php programming. We offer our technology skills to help our customers with their questions on php programming.</p>\r\n<p><b>J2EE/.NET Application Architecture Consulting </b></p>\r\n<p>Technology Architecture is a critical determining factor of business survival and success. A good architecture provides a plan for managing IT investments that is aligned with business objectives. Millettech\'s architecture consulting services help our clients to be capable of aligning technology with the big picture. Which focus on application solutions with J2EE and .NET that deliver total business integration .We offer our technology skills, and enterprise application expertise to help our customers extend, enhance, and leverage their existing and new IT investments. We provide our customers with the solutions and technology infrastructure that delivers not only cost advantages, but also, lasting strategic value.</p><br>','Technical Services','','publish','closed','closed','','technical-services','','','2018-01-19 15:24:22','2018-01-19 07:24:22','',0,'http://test.milettech.com/?page_id=131',0,'page','',0),(132,1,'2018-01-19 15:24:22','2018-01-19 07:24:22','<p><b>Technical Consulting</b></p>\r\n<p><b>PHP Application Consulting</b></p>\r\n<p>PHP is world\'s fastest growing web development language and Millettech specializes in this scripting language. We have many years experience in website designing and development with php programming. We offer our technology skills to help our customers with their questions on php programming.</p>\r\n<p><b>J2EE/.NET Application Architecture Consulting </b></p>\r\n<p>Technology Architecture is a critical determining factor of business survival and success. A good architecture provides a plan for managing IT investments that is aligned with business objectives. Millettech\'s architecture consulting services help our clients to be capable of aligning technology with the big picture. Which focus on application solutions with J2EE and .NET that deliver total business integration .We offer our technology skills, and enterprise application expertise to help our customers extend, enhance, and leverage their existing and new IT investments. We provide our customers with the solutions and technology infrastructure that delivers not only cost advantages, but also, lasting strategic value.</p><br>','Technical Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','131-revision-v1','','','2018-01-19 15:24:22','2018-01-19 07:24:22','',131,'http://test.milettech.com/?p=132',0,'revision','',0),(133,1,'2018-01-19 1